data.description: Buy This Home and We'll Sell Yours For Free!  Welcome to this stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with 1,674 square feet of living space! Built in 2018, this home has all the your looking for in your dream home. Upon entering the home, you are greeted with a spacious and open floor plan that combines the living and dining areas for the perfect family and entertainment space. The big kitchen is the heart of this home and features modern appliances, plenty of counter space, a lot of cabinets for your organizational needs, and a nice spacious pantry. The vinyl flooring throughout the house provides a warm and comfortable feeling while also being easy to maintain and clean. The bathrooms are adorned with beautiful tile flooring that adds a touch of elegance to the space. The vaulted ceiling in the living room adds to the charm and modern aesthetic of the home while also providing an airy and spacious atmosphere. The great curb appeal of this home exudes its stylish and inviting presence. The big backyard is a wonderful addition to the home, and it provides ample outdoor space for entertaining, family gatherings, and activities. Gutters all around the home ensure that the exterior of the house is kept clean, and the inground saltwater pool provides a refreshing space to relax and cool off on a hot summer day. The nice patio is perfect for outdoor barbecues and enjoying the beautiful Florida sunsets. Additionally, a shed in the backyard provides extra storage space for all your outdoor items. The fully fenced backyard offers privacy and security with easy and safe access to your outdoor oasis. Located in the lovely Matanzas Woods neighborhood, this home offers convenient access to schools, parks, shopping, and dining options. Commuting is a breeze with major highways and public transportation just a short distance away! This home is an absolute must-see, and a rare opportunity to own an immaculate and move-in ready pool home. Seller's are motivated to sell so don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and elegance this property has to offer.
